# Lint/type-check tooling for the CI "lint" job.
# Compiled to lint.txt with hashes via: make pip-compile
#
# The runtime dep (mcp) is included so mypy --strict can resolve the FastMCP
# types rather than treating them as untyped. ruff/black are pinned to the
# exact versions the CI lint job uses so the check stays deterministic across
# uv recompiles.
